name: User Productivity by Claims Submitted and Charges
description: This report will help you measure the performance of any user processing claims. You can see the number of claims processed and the charges for each claim according to the time you performed the task per specific day.

name: Auditing of Changes by User Report
description: Use this report to audit your team's activity in different time ranges. Monitoring your team's performance could help you obtain accurate results from your operations.

name: Health Professional Productivity by Patients, Claims, and Charges
description:
Use this report to draw valuable conclusions regarding the productivity of Health Professionals.
The efficiency of this report consists of verifying how productive the services were in terms of billing amounts.
This report will be helpful for clients who have health professionals in their healthcare company or independent health professionals

name: Number of Claims by Company and Current Status
description: Use this report to consult the number of claims by company and filtered by statuses. This report will help to you to make decisions in your current claim processing flow.
